title.rendered: Arnold Schwarzenegger Previews Terminator: Genisys in Muscle & Fitness

content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

Arnold Schwarzenegger is about to make a dramatic return to the iconic Terminator franchise, and he gave Muscle & Fitness an exclusive sneak peek.

He’ll be back … and here’s our first look!

The legendary actor-turned-politician-turned actor took Muscle & Fitness Editor-in-Chief Shawn Perine behind the scenes of Terminator: Genisys.

It’s been 12 years, but Arnold hasn’t missed a beat, as evidenced by the workout secrets and exclusive photos he shared in between scenes.

In addition to this video, first posted via Radar Online, Muscle & Fitness also offers insight into hard-hitting training programs and recipes.

Ones fit for a Terminator? You know it.
